HEADWORD: Accurst
<hw>Ac*curst"</hw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>p. p. & a.</pos> <def>Doomed to destruction
or misery; cursed; hence, bad enough to be under the curse; execrable;
detestable; exceedingly hateful; -- <as>as, an <ex>accursed</ex>
deed</as>.</def> <au>Shak.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Ac*curs"ed*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Ac*curs"ed*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Accusable</ent>⟦br⟧
